    "body": "@pbirbarah Before I deployed the contract and invoked the `test` function on localhost through truffle console and ganache-cli I was able to successfully invoke `test` through the test suite by configuring a init test file and executing the ```truffle test``` command\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst TestPayment = artifacts.require(\"TestPayment\");\r\n\r\ncontract(\"TestPayment\", (accounts) => {\r\n  it(\"Should invoke the test() function\", async () => {\r\n    const testPayment = await TestPayment.deployed();\r\n\r\n    await testPayment.test({ value: 1e15 });\r\n  });\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\n<img width=\"877\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-06-07 at 4 38 27 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42893948/172477959-ee90b567-bd17-41dd-b4b8-3e68f5589a1b.png\">\r\n\r\n",
